channel.title: Fixing Doors and Tele Locs. Coordinates needed
channel.description:
Ok so me and my mates on my clan server have spent the last week fixing all doors, teleports, and such around our server. yet we're still missing some coordinates to key locations. Such as..
Keldagrim (not the area above, the actual city underground, and not the entrance either) underground temple to morytania = nature spirit quest thing. (the area where the chamber guardian dog resides) Zaro's Temple in Digsite (you know in the quest where you use the rope on the winch to lower yourself down.)
If anyone has these coords, i'd really appreciate it. Not the above ground locations. because as you may or may not be aware, just because the entrance to something is above ground somewhere, doesn't mean the location is right underneath it. Soo.. if you happen to find these coords. thx.
